com.epam.training.bean

Class Issue

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.epam.training.bean.Entity
      • com.epam.training.bean.Issue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Issue
extends Entity
    Class Issue is a Java Bean that stores the data of issues reported in the application (id, summary, description, status, priority, type, project, assignee, etc.).
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
